---
// GuaranteeSection — risk reversal that lives directly above the audit form.
// $100 promise is the visual anchor; 14-day refund window backs the project work.
---
<!-- GUARANTEE SECTION -->
<section class="relative border-b border-line">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="card relative overflow-hidden p-7 sm:p-10 lg:p-12">
      <div class="accent-glow absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-[420px] h-[420px]" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Left: $100 anchor -->
        <div class="lg:pt-2">
          <div class="relative inline-flex flex-col items-start gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-accent/40 bg-accent/10 px-6 py-5 sm:px-8 sm:py-6 shadow-[0_20px_50px_-20px_rgba(255,107,26,0.45)]">
            <span class="font-display text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">If we can't find 3</span>
            <span class="font-display font-bold text-[3.5rem] sm:text-[4.2rem] lg:text-[5rem] leading-none text-text">
              <span class="text-accent">$</span>100
            </span>
            <span class="font-display text-[0.78rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-text-soft">For your time</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: copy -->
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Risk Reversal</span>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.6rem] leading-[1.05] font-bold tracking-tight">
            A Simple Guarantee Before You<br class="hidden sm:block"/> Spend a Dollar
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-text-soft text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed">
            We don't want you guessing whether your website, Google presence, or quote flow is costing you leads. That's why every Founding Client starts with a free Lead Leak Audit.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-4 text-text text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed">
            If we can't find <span class="text-accent font-semibold">at least 3 specific lead leaks</span> that may be costing your business calls, quote requests, or booked jobs, we'll send you <span class="text-accent font-semibold">$100 for wasting your time</span>.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-4 text-text-soft text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed">
            If you decide to work with us, you'll have <span class="text-text font-medium">14 days after the project starts</span> to make sure you feel good about the direction. If the work doesn't match what we agreed on, we'll make it right or refund your project payment.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-4 text-text-soft text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed">
            No weird pressure. No mystery marketing fluff. Just a clear look at what's helping your business grow and what's quietly holding it back.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="#audit-form" class="btn-primary">
              Claim My Founding 5 Spot
              <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /GUARANTEE SECTION -->
